  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new card based action adventure rpg set in the world of Caelum. Embark into a mysterious journey full of secrets and collect powerful cards to solve the riddles of this epic land and battle with other collectors!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/b78bc7fe837ba03227beb9ec37088c3b.poster.avif?t=1744392942\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/b78bc7fe837ba03227beb9ec37088c3b.webm?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/b78bc7fe837ba03227beb9ec37088c3b.mp4?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• A Nonlinear world experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world that expands into multiple directions where you are free to make choices and decide your own path as a collector and adventurer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/1bcd6ee7b1338aa30e6f6a1b125f4b56.poster.avif?t=1744392942\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/1bcd6ee7b1338aa30e6f6a1b125f4b56.webm?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/1bcd6ee7b1338aa30e6f6a1b125f4b56.mp4?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• A riddle-full world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each corner may hide an enemy, a puzzle or a secret. Traverse with caution! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.poster.avif?t=1744392942\" width=616 height=520 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.webm?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.mp4?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Cards are your weapons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the elements of the cards in the open world to take advantage of situations or make a powerful quick hand to take any collector out of your way!</p>",
