h corner may hide an enemy, a puzzle or a secret. Traverse with caution! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.poster.avif?t=1744392942\" width=616 height=520 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.webm?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.mp4?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Cards are your weapons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the elements of the cards in the open world to take advantage of situations or make a powerful quick hand to take any collector out of your way!</p>",
